originalText.text: Stay clear of these rip-off artists. And arrogant jerks to boot. Like to give 0 stars, but 1 is the least google has.  Sad thing is, the location is awesome, but the service, and particularly the employee, is lousy. Reserved through Spot Hero. Gives absolutely no indication of a $20 “Oversized Vehicle” extra charge on the app, even after putting in my vehicle information on the app. Blind sided by the charge upon pickup. Confronted him about the charge and it not saying anything about oversized vehicles on the app, and the guy got belligerent, told me to get a smaller vehicle, and said that “I should have known” it was an oversized vehicle, even though it said nothing about extra charges for an suv on the app. These jerks are unethical, rude, arrogant, among other adjectives I’d like to use but I am keeping it PG.

originalText.text: Very delightful parking experience there. A very nice guy took good care of my SUV. I went shopping on 5th Ave and got an appointment that I was gonna be late for. I entered the garage in a hurry and a gentleman took care of my car with valet parking very well. He checked together with me the scars on my car before park in. So that I can confirm no new scars when pick it up. Not sure what happened to others in the review and certainly I can’t speak of others. But for my parking experience there it’s delighted and there’s no too much waiting. Great and nice guy taking care of my car there!

originalText.text: The employee is a scammer. He checked my reservation online and took the car's key, parked my car. When I came back in a few hours later he said that my reservation was at a different address at a different garage and I need to pay $64 instead of $39 I've already paid via HeroSpot app. He was grinning and it looks like they have a fraudulent scheme.

originalText.text: HORRIBLE and I mean HORRIBLE customer service. I made a reservation online at this place and when I arrived the attendant said it was “FULL”. I explained to him that I had prepaid the reservation already but he didn’t care. He then got aggressive and threatened to fight me. I called the police for his threats. The police arrived and informed that he had quit. What type of employees does this place hire. DONT PARK HERE
